-- Santam to Buy Balance of Indwe Broker for $35 Million from Pamodzi, Thebe
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-06-28T13:35:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/santam-to-buy-balance-of-indwe-broker-for-35-million-from-pamodzi-thebe.html

          
          
             Santam Ltd., South Africa’s largest
property and casualty insurer, said it agreed to buy the shares
it doesn’t already own in Indwe Broker Holdings Group Ltd. for
263.4 million rand.  
 Santam, which owns 47.32 percent of Indwe, will buy 26.34
percent of the company from Pamodzi Investment Corp. Ltd. and
Thebe Investment Corp. Ltd.  
          
          


  


        